rniture US‚Äôs ability to create not only contemporary\n        spaces but also refined, classic interiors tailored to each client‚Äôs unique vision.\n      <\/p>\n\n      <p>\n        The grand main living room was centered around a <strong>173‚Äù custom Chesterfield sofa<\/strong>, crafted to\n        perfectly fit the room‚Äôs proportions. To complement it, we paired <strong>hand-carved armchairs<\/strong>,\n        blending artisanal craftsmanship with timeless style. With ceilings twice the standard height, we designed and\n        produced <strong>custom-made drapery<\/strong> that emphasized the vertical grandeur of the space. At the\n        entrance, a <strong>custom-designed rug<\/strong> was created to set a sophisticated tone upon arrival.\n      <\/p>\n\n      <p>\n        In the dining room, we incorporated a <strong>luxurious porcelain dining table<\/strong> paired with elegant\n        classical detailing, creating a space ideal for formal gatherings. Throughout the home, every element‚Äîfrom\n        finishes to furniture‚Äîwas carefully selected to balance traditional charm with functional comfort.\n      <\/p>\n\n      <p>\n        This project underscores Saloni Furniture US‚Äôs versatility, demonstrating that our custom design services can\n        cater to a wide range of aesthetics‚Äîfrom modern minimalism to timeless classicism.\n      <\/p>\n\n      <p><strong class=\"team\">Project Team:<\/strong><\/p>\n\n      <ul>\n        <li><strong>Architect:<\/strong> Emre Ozkaya<\/li>\n        <li><strong>Lead Designer:<\/strong> Sirin Ozdemir<\/li>\n        <li><strong>Project Manager:<\/strong> Harun Uzulmez<\/li>\n        <li><strong>3D Visualization Artist:<\/strong> Kadir Aydinli<\/li>\n      <\/ul>\n\n      <p>\n        With <strong>B.K. Residence,<\/strong> every detail reflects the client‚Äôs passion for tradition while showcasing Saloni‚Äôs ability\n        to craft personalized, high-quality interiors that stand the test of time.\n      <\/